3 cups oatmeal
1/4 cup flour
1/4 cup brown sugar
1 cup nuts (walnuts, slivered almonds, pumpkin seeds etc)
2 tsp cinnamon
1/2 tsp ginger
3 tbs oil (unflavoured like vegetable, not olive)
3 tbs honey/maple syrup 
1/4 cup orange juice

Line cookie sheet with parchment paper. Bake 15 min at 350 degrees turning once.
